---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Personal Care – Aion HCSS">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading text-navy">Personal Care</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-700">Dignified support with daily living activities, tailored to your routines and preferences.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-heading text-navy">What’s included</h2>
    <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 text-slate-700 space-y-1">
      <li>Assistance with personal tasks and daily personal hygiene</li>
      <li>Medication management and reminders</li>
      <li>Mobility and transfer assistance</li>
      <li>Meal planning and preparation</li>
      <li>Light domestic tasks, cleaning and laundry</li>
      <li>Companionship and emotional support</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4">
      <a href="tel:01245823377" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-coral px-6 py-3 font-medium text-navy">Call 01245823377</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-slate-300 px-6 py-3">Enquire online</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
